title: Video: Natas Loves You â€“ Skip Stones
content:
Cross-country five piece Natas Loves You formed in Luxembourg, but its members hail from in and around Paris. The new video for track Skip Stones features footage of a trip to India and serves as a perfect backdrop to the slick production and infectiously catchy hook. Think Passion Pit mashed with MGMT, with a little Metronomy thrown in for good measure. In other words, perfect daytime festival music.

You can watch the video for Skip Stones above
